---
title: Carb Smart Tofu Salad with Croutons and Dill Pickle Cream
description: Another salad, you say?! But this isn't just any salad. Dill pickle cream dolloped over BBQ-seasoned tofu livens up this full plate of veggies. Quick, simple and delicious!

